Package jaco.swing.autocomplete

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CompletionProvider<E>
    A CompletionProvider is used to connect to a data source for providing completions for Autocomplete based on the content typed by the user.
    ItemValueConverter<E>
    Interface for converting a CompletionProvider's completion object to a String representation to display in the Autocomplete's menu.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Autocomplete<E>
    Autocomplete widget is used to auto-complete a user's keystrokes by providing self-defined, context-sensitive completions in a drop-down menu.
    DefaultCompletionProvider<E>
    The default completion provider whose data source is backed by a given collection.
    TokenChangedEvent
    An event that is fired when a completion token has changed.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Autocomplete.CompletionBoundary
    Constants for configuring the Autocomplete's rule to parse a completion token up to a specific boundary.
